{"tid":81323,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"個半月歐遊（瑞士荷蘭德國意大利冰島芬蘭英國）","createTime":"2017-01-15T08:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T14:51:33.000Z","uid":55556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b610bed78c866e3a7a4e857acd6581f1cffa02a","tid":81323,"uid":55556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:35:48.000Z","msg":"19打工仔一個<br />\n咁啱女朋友去exchange<br />\n又咁啱我唔想做<br />\n索性辭職去陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已返黎，打返遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日<br />\n瑞士航空直飛蘇黎世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbYt57Ve6bME7628jiGwuisTBwQ4ZgjCtNdxb98EFnQ1L?filename=zR96N84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzR96N84.jpg&h=5972daa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要坐成13個鐘，真係坐到屎忽都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPzSYw3oTevNfdCkUXqyHW4NvaEphHYsDjKztmUANYKJf?filename=v74SNhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv74SNhX.jpg&h=2a61edde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/162345_af0244c8ec2e25a786de1660d4ad030b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F162345_af0244c8ec2e25a786de1660d4ad030b.jpg&h=9271767e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休息下就去蘇黎世河兩邊行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n河邊真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdBL6vSgCgKto9uE6LMuctTz4B1YLLUoNxn4sTsXM2F7J?filename=p6870A3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6870A3.jpg&h=a161eae8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/162422_ffb17260774e1688256c4bc21a1ed9cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F162422_ffb17260774e1688256c4bc21a1ed9cb.jpg&h=45a4d278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbCqL3xmUW43b1X2CgEuLB6evRgANkpj5WUfecbJyeZjZ?filename=MU848U1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMU848U1.jpg&h=37485a62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/162423_870cf125fca329c86bcf7e182d031d91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F162423_870cf125fca329c86bcf7e182d031d91.jpg&h=fc73ff51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbawXaRwzEeTqsPiFRm9t3d35FpZFoiTzUFqrLCbwPCkn?filename=551Ye77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F551Ye77.jpg&h=1e7461bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左好似油炸鬼既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/163458_1c79c8677747e0427d09e07051eb8f11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F163458_1c79c8677747e0427d09e07051eb8f11.jpg&h=9867e306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去瑞士梗係要買瑞士軍刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/163405_61700822747f1c5f2d70b2e35915c003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F163405_61700822747f1c5f2d70b2e35915c003.jpg&h=9937d66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然係2015年版，但係我覺得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點女友送<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎瑞士落一落腳，因為好快就去荷蘭阿姆斯特丹<br />\n，再去完德國再返瑞士"},{"pid":"0487f0d89229c688d0f87f94a6a6306ad4c1965d","tid":81323,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"荷蘭撚留名"},{"pid":"b62f279f06749279248f70343aa9de38643285bb","tid":81323,"uid":65885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"留名 打算暑假去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758c3909eec295154c16829aa0dc95fcc634cc8c","tid":81323,"uid":73823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"長居歐洲 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03978489e0fb63c3edbc13474253c0fe5eaa1d8","tid":81323,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"瑞士軍刀 更係自己襯色刻名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dfb7533f5a8ea5bfb32061fc84f66b6d7c35be","tid":81323,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"洗左幾錢"},{"pid":"9a542f69c1b616db715c84a81cbf3a7e8e767079","tid":81323,"uid":55556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞士軍刀 更係自己襯色刻名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d5b841e38051439b45e85bdd2e81055b65f6bd","tid":81323,"uid":55556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗左幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntotal 3萬幾"},{"pid":"e373241f110a66baf810ee461ccc4a66c97dda2e","tid":81323,"uid":26703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:43:5